      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Hard to knock the consistency of ALDEBARAN ABEL (8) who has added to a string of top-four results by clocking in second in his last two outings here. Shouldn't spend a penny from this draw and the sprint lane may come in handy. Could break through. SKY FLAIR (2) hasn't raced since a midfield finish in the Breeders Crown 3F Final here seven months ago but was readied with a trial win. Hasn't missed a place when fresh and draws well. NO MONEY NO HONEY (5) was let down by manners in both outings of last campaign and has changed yards since. Close-up in a recent trial and has won at this circuit and distance before so can make an immediate impact. PARIS KAY (3) is up in grade but should be respected after scoring from this barrier last start at Ballarat.",
